{"prompt": "Generate a website for a online magazine. The website should be clean and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Online Magazine</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #4a90e2; /* Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #85b7f0;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-footer-bg: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #cccccc 1px solid;\n        }\n\n        header a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n\n        header ul {\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            list-style: none;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header li {\n            float: left;\n            display: inline;\n            padding: 0 20px 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header #branding {\n            float: left;\n        }\n\n        header #branding h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        header nav {\n            float: right;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding-top: 60px;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.7), rgba(74, 144, 226, 0.7));\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h1 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 55px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.4;\n        }\n\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n\n        .article {\n            background: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .article h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            color: #777777;\n        }\n\n        .btn-primary {\n            display: inline-block;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .btn-primary:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        @media(max-width: 768px){\n            header #branding,\n            header nav,\n            header nav ul li{\n                float: none;\n                text-align: center;\n                width: 100%;\n            }\n            header nav ul li{\n                padding: 10px;\n            }\n            .hero-section h1 {\n                font-size: 40px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div id=\"branding\">\n                <h1>Online Magazine</h1>\n            </div>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">Home</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">Politics</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">Technology</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">Lifestyle</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#\">About</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Discover Today's Stories</h1>\n            <p>Your daily dose of news, insights, and inspiration.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"main-content\">\n            <article class=\"article\">\n                <h3>Latest Tech Breakthroughs</h3>\n                <p>A new AI model promises to revolutionize natural language processing, offering unprecedented accuracy and understanding.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn-primary\">Read More</a>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"article\">\n                <h3>The Future of Remote Work</h3>\n                <p>As companies adapt, we explore the long-term implications of flexible work arrangements on productivity and employee well-being.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn-primary\">Read More</a>\n            </article>\n            <article class=\"article\">\n                <h3>Sustainable Living Tips</h3>\n                <p>Simple changes you can make in your daily life to reduce your environmental footprint and contribute to a healthier planet.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn-primary\">Read More</a>\n            </article>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Online Magazine. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}